@node usage "usage"
                                 @{b}Usage@{ub}
           1.Run PuK-Lottery
            
            2.Wait for Randomizer Function to Initilize after startup.

              3.click on small ball button next to play
         
                4. thats all goodluck.

                  5. to exit click on x button (bottom right)
@endnode

